<i>the article on An Da-hye's been posted.</i>

21
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:28,440
<i>…up to 71%.</i>

22
00:02:28,524 --> 00:02:32,403
<i>It was mostly influenced by Shandong,</i>
<i>which is in the same latitude.</i>

23
00:02:32,486 --> 00:02:35,656
<i>Today, the Central Bank's</i>
<i>Monetary Policy Committee</i>

24
