<i>set the fixed interest rate at 3.9%.</i>

25
00:02:37,575 --> 00:02:41,579
<i>The economic growth rate</i>
<i>appears to be 2.6%,</i>

26
00:02:41,662 --> 00:02:43,831
<i>which is 0.2 points higher</i>
<i>than three months ago.</i>

27
00:02:43,914 --> 00:02:46,876
<i>As the economy is becoming stable…</i>

28
00:02:46,959 --> 00:02:50,296
<i>What a great morning</i>
<i>to start drinking again</i>

29
00:02:50,379 --> 00:02:54,008
<i>after I quit because of you, Seo Ji-woo.</i>

30
00:02:57,303 --> 00:02:58,512
It's hot!

31
00:02:59,388 --> 00:03:00,389
Damn it!

32
00:03:01,473 --> 00:03:04,268
<i>Actress An Da-hye's alleged affair</i>
<i>raises suspicion.</i>

33
00:03:04,351 --> 00:03:07,396
<i>The man involved</i>
<i>is the second son of conglomerate A.</i>

34
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:10,399
<i>The main issue</i>
<i>is the suspicion of An Da-hye's drug use.</i>

35
00:03:10,482 --> 00:03:12,776
<i>I'll cooperate fully</i>
<i>with the investigation.</i>

36
00:03:13,903 --> 00:03:15,738
<i>When An was taking drugs…</i>

37
00:03:15,821 --> 00:03:18,449
<i>Seochang Group's second son, Cho Jin-eon…</i>

38
00:03:18,532 --> 00:03:20,326
<i>Fuck off. Get that out of my sight.</i>

39
00:03:20,409 --> 00:03:22,703
<i>- The prosecution is investigating.</i>
<i>- Cho's wife, Seo…</i>

40
00:03:22,786 --> 00:03:25,372
<i>- Even to Seo Ji-woo…</i>
<i>- Seo Ji-woo's husband, Cho…</i>

41
00:03:25,456 --> 00:03:27,249
<i>JARIM Apparel's second daughter…</i>

42
00:03:27,333 --> 00:03:29,126
<i>- Seo has…</i>
<i>- JARIM's second daughter…</i>

43
00:03:29,209 --> 00:03:31,378
<i>- Seo's marriage is…</i>
<i>- An Da-hye did drugs.</i>

44
00:03:31,462 --> 00:03:33,964
<i>It could become an owner-level risk</i>
<i>for JARIM Apparel.</i>

45
00:03:34,048 --> 00:03:36,300
<i>- Seo Ji-woo's JARIM Apparel…</i>
<i>- Seo Ji-woo is…</i>

46
00:03:36,383 --> 00:03:37,968
<i>The public is paying attention.</i>

47
00:03:39,637 --> 00:03:41,430
Now that I've lived long enough,

48
00:03:41,513 --> 00:03:43,933
I wonder how one's life
can be that turbulent.

49
00:03:44,642 --> 00:03:47,561
I mean, why can't she just live quietly?

50
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:51,607
Why did she have to marry
a jerk like him of all men? Jeez.

51
